{"lemma":"قَرّاب","slug":"قَرّاب","root":"ق.ر.ب","root_slug":"ق-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ر-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35402","n35403","n35404","n35411"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%91%D8%A7%D8%A8"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35402","headword_ar":"قَرَابٌ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobN","text_ar":"قُرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", former half."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n35403","headword_ar":"قُرَابٌ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qariybN","text_ar":"قَرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last quarter, in two places: ―         -b2-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobN","text_ar":"قُرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", near the middle: ―         -b3-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiraAbN","text_ar":"قِرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", former half: ―         -b4-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quraAbapN","text_ar":"قُرَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n35404","headword_ar":"قِرَابٌ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[an inf. n. of 3. And hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiraAba","text_ar":"قِرَابَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as an adv. n. of time]. You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuhu qiraAba AlEi$aA='i","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُهُ قِرَابَ العِشَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came to him near nightfall:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiraAba All~ayoli","text_ar":"قِرَابَ اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA.) And 'Oweyf El-Kawáfee says, describing she-camels, (so in the TA and in one of my copies of the S,) or 'Oweyf El-Fezáree, (so in the O,)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"huwa A@bonu munaD~ijaAtK kun~a qidomFA\n                      \n                     \n                        yazidona EalaY AlEadiydi qiraAba $ahorK"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is the off spring of"},{"kind":"text","text":"[one of the]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she-camels that went beyond the usual time of bringing forth, that used formely to exceed the computed"},{"kind":"text","text":"[time]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near a month:"},{"kind":"text","text":"J give a different reading of this verse,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaridona EalaY Algadiyir","text_ar":"يَرِدْنَ عَلَى الغَدِيِر"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but the correct reading is that given above. (IB, TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobN","text_ar":"قُرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", near the middle. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiraAbu Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"قِرَابُ الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quraAbuhu","text_ar":"قُرَابُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quraAbatuhu","text_ar":"قُرَابَتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is nearly the equal in quantity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amount,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nearly the equivalent, of the thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEahu A^alofu dirohamK A^awo qiraAbuhu","text_ar":"مَعَهُ اَلْفُ دِرْهَمٍ اَوْ قِرَابُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has with him a thousand dirhems, or nearly the equal thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEahu milo'u qadaHK maA='F A^awo qiraAbuhu","text_ar":"مَعَهُ مِلْءُ قَدَحٍ مَا=ءً اَوْ قِرَابُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has with him a cupful of water, or nearly the equal thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA.) And a poet says, (S,) namely, El- 'Ambar, (so in the O and TA,) or Es-Sinnabr, (so in the Mz, 49th"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nwE","text_ar":"نوع"},{"kind":"text","text":",) Ibn-'Amr, Ibn-Temeem, (O, TA, *)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A_il~aA tajiy^o maloA^aY yajiy^o qiraAbuhaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If a full"},{"kind":"text","text":"bucket ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dalowN","text_ar":"دَلْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being understood, as is indicated in the S and O and TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"come not, what will be nearly the equal thereof will come"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O, TA.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lawo A^an~a liY qiraAba h`*aA","text_ar":"لَوْ اَنَّ لِى قِرَابَ هٰذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahabFA","text_ar":"ذَهَبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If there belonged to me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the quantity nearly sufficient for the filling of this"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of gold"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lawo jaA='a biqiraAbi AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"لَوْ جَا=ءَ بِقِرَابِ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If he brought"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which would be nearly the equal in quantity of the earth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~ukobatayoni","text_ar":"الرُّكْبَتَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaA='u quraAbapu","text_ar":"المَا=ءُ قُرَابَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The water is such as is nearly the equal in height of the two knees"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qarabapN","text_ar":"قَرَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gimod","text_ar":"غِمْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scabbard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheath,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a sword, (K, TA,) or of a knife: (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jafon","text_ar":"جَفْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"receptacle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gimod","text_ar":"غِمْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jafon","text_ar":"جَفْن"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"receptacle, wherein is the sword together with its scabbard"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bigimodihi","text_ar":"بِغِمْدِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and its suspensory belt"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cord:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA:) it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiraAb","text_ar":"جِرَاب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of leather, into which the rider,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rider upon a camel, puts his sword with its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jafon","text_ar":"جَفْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scabbard"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and his whip, and his staff,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stick, and his utensils:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiraAb","text_ar":"جِرَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into which one puts his sword with its scabbard"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bigimodihi","text_ar":"بِغِمْدِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and his whip, and sometimes his travelling-provisions of dates &c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, TA:) the pl. of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiraAb","text_ar":"قِرَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the sword is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurubN","text_ar":"قُرُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of mult.] (Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqoribapN","text_ar":"اَقْرِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of pauc.], like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xumurN","text_ar":"خُمُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axomirapN","text_ar":"اَخْمِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"pls. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximaArN","text_ar":"خِمَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurobN","text_ar":"قُرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", latter half."}],"source_refs":["O","TA","S","K","Az","IAth","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n35411","headword_ar":"قَرَّابٌ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A maker of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what are called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qrb","text_ar":"قرب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurub","text_ar":"قُرُب"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiraAbN","text_ar":"قِرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or perhaps"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirab","text_ar":"قِرَب"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirobapN","text_ar":"قِرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}